('Technology', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/10812427-L.jpg', 'Andi Diehn', 'Technology: Cool Women Who Code combines high-interest content with links to online primary sources and essential questions that further expand kids knowledge and understanding of a topic they come in contact with every day. Compelling portraits of women who have excelled in meeting the challenges of their field keep kids interested and infused with a sense of possibility and determination.', 2015, NOW(), NOW()),
