('Introduction to Urban Water Distribution, Second Edition', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13205922-L.jpg', 'Nemanja Trifunovic', 'Published in 2020, this work explores themes of Introduction to Urban Water Distribution, Second Edition.', 2020, NOW(), NOW()),
