('Engineering Applications of Neural Networks', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/9739982-L.jpg', 'Lazaros Iliadis', 'Published in 2011, this work explores themes of Engineering Applications of Neural Networks.', 2011, NOW(), NOW()),
