('Excel 2016 for Dummies Book + Online Videos Bundle', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/10282402-L.jpg', 'Greg Harvey', '"Whether you''re starting from square one or updating your skills, this hands-on guide to Excel 2016 gets you up and running--fast. You''ll easily get the hand of worksheets, formulas, graphs, formatting,a nd more as you explore this powerful, versatile application. Show off your data and maximize its potential!" -- Page [4] cover.', 2015, NOW(), NOW()),
