('Introduction to Sociology', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/7398317-L.jpg', 'OpenStax College', 'Introduction to Sociology is intended for a one-semester introductory sociology course. Conceived of and developed by active sociology instructors, this up-to-date title and can be downloaded now by clicking on the "Get this book" button below. This online, fully editable and customizable title includes sociology theory and research; real-world applications; simplify and debate features; and learning objectives for each chapter.', 2012, NOW(), NOW()),
