('Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第一章 王都の一日編 2', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/14022168-L.jpg', 'Daichi Matsuse', 'Subaru Natsuki had just been trying to get to the convenience store, but he wound up summoned to another world. Worse, he has only one special ability, and he has to die to use it! At least now he''s got a goal--save the girl with the silver hair and bring a smile to her face. But how many times is he going to have to die a terrible death in order to make that goal a reality?', 2016, NOW(), NOW()),
('Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第二章 屋敷の一週間編 4', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/14235848-L.jpg', 'Daichi Matsuse', 'To save himself from another cycle of death and rebirth, Subaru must confront the beast in the forest. But what will happen to him there when his dear friend Rem snaps?', 2017, NOW(), NOW()),
