('Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第三章 Truth of Zero 9', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/9255471-L.jpg', '長月達平', 'Published in 2019, this work explores themes of Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第三章 Truth of Zero 9.', 2019, NOW(), NOW()),
('Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第三章 Truth of Zero 1', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13562536-L.jpg', 'Daichi Matsuse', 'Subaru returns with Emilia to the capital of Lugunica, where it all started for him. There, he runs into some (unfortunately) familiar faces ... but also the other candidates for Queen of Lugunica!', 2017, NOW(), NOW()),
('Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第三章 Truth of Zero 2', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13562235-L.jpg', 'Daichi Matsuse', 'Published in 2018, this work explores themes of Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第三章 Truth of Zero 2.', 2018, NOW(), NOW()),
('Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第三章 Truth of Zero 3', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13562429-L.jpg', 'Daichi Matsuse', '"Whether in a dinner with royal candidate Crusch Karsten or another sparring session with master swordsman Wilhelm, Subaru is often reminded that he has much to learn. However, the opportunity for reflection is cut short when Rem senses peril at Roswaal Manor. Never one to sit still, Subaru races back to the mansion, but what awaits him is not for the faint of heart..."--Back page.', 2018, NOW(), NOW()),
('怪獣8号 3', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/12978272-L.jpg', '松本直也', 'Published in 2022, this work explores themes of 怪獣8号 3.', 2022, NOW(), NOW()),
('Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第三章 Truth of Zero 6', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/10328383-L.jpg', 'Daichi Matsuse', 'Published in 2019, this work explores themes of Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第三章 Truth of Zero 6.', 2019, NOW(), NOW()),
('ダンダダン 1', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/14554208-L.jpg', '龍幸伸', 'Published in 2022, this work explores themes of ダンダダン 1.', 2022, NOW(), NOW()),
('Bibi Blocksberg', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/10843808-L.jpg', 'Olivia Vieweg', '###German-language description Auf zur Geisterjagd! Bibi hat ihr Versprechen gehalten und ist mit Miyu nach Japan geflogen! Dort ist alles neu und aufregend, vor allem wenn bei Miyus Eltern das Telefon klingelt, denn dann ist Yokai-Alarm! Überall, wo die kleinen Geister auftauchen, verursachen sie ordentlich Ärger. Bibi ist fest entschlossen: Sie will Miyu und ihren Eltern helfen! Ihr gemeinsames Abenteuer führt sie diesmal in die schrille Modewelt Japans! Aber Achtung: Die Yokai sind nicht weit … ---------- ###English-language description: Young witch Bibi Blocksberg was ecstatic when her new friend Miyu invited her to stay with her family in Japan for a cultural exchange trip. Unfortunately, ghost hunting keeps them too busy for any sight seeing, but a much-needed break for some karaoke fun leads Bibi to realize that Miyu is an amazing singer. With a big contest about to be held in Kyoto, the two magical girls must figure out how to keep the city safe from otherworldly spirits while preparing for the show.', 2020, NOW(), NOW()),
('BLACK CLOVER Vol.28 [Japanese Edition]', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/10831984-L.jpg', 'Yūki Tabata', 'Published in 2021, this work explores themes of BLACK CLOVER Vol.28 [Japanese Edition].', 2021, NOW(), NOW()),
('The Heart of a Warrior', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/9329747-L.jpg', 'Erin Hunter', 'Ravenpaw and Barley helped their friends in ThunderClan defeat the vicious BloodClan cats in Twolegplace. Now they''re ready to fight to reclaim their home on the farm. Firestar has promised to send a warrior patrol to assist them, but Ravenpaw worries that it won''t be enough to chase out the invaders. He knows that he must find his courage and fight like a warrior - or lose his home forever. ---------- Books in this series 1. [Shattered Peace][1] 2. [A Clan in Need][2] 3. The Heart of a Warrior [1]: https://openlibrary.org/works/OL17438399W [2]: https://openlibrary.org/works/OL17430318W', 2010, NOW(), NOW()),
('ONE PIECE DOORS! 3', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/11225478-L.jpg', '尾田栄一郎', 'ONE PIECEのトビラ絵　カサネ読×新セカイ 第599話〜第862話の215枚で大構成!!! 連載7年分を収録　JC26巻分の白黒扉絵を掲載！　めくれば“織り上がる新世界”！ アニマル劇場　愛獣凶獣with麦わらの一味！　読者リクエストでさらに賑やか!! 短期集中表紙連載　“ルフィが出ないONE PIECE”!?　伏線＆考察記事つきで4編収録。', 2019, NOW(), NOW()),
('Coyote', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/11886981-L.jpg', 'Sei Awata', 'Coyote reúne quatro histórias que se passam em um futuro onde alta tecnologia e uma sociedade decadente se misturam. É nesse cenário que conhecemos Alícia, uma prostituta que sonha com o “mundo externo”, mas tem assuntos inacabados com um de seus clientes. Também vemos um gentil Worker, um androide trabalhador, que acaba envolvido em um movimento contra os humanos. As relações entre uma família de super-heróis, onde só a irmão do meio não possui poderes, é revelada nas páginas de Coyote. Para fechar, conhecemos um “temido demônio” que fora trancafiado e agora, solto, quer se vingar de seu algoz.', 2014, NOW(), NOW()),
('おたくの隣りはエルフですか？ 1', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/14420652-L.jpg', 'Meguru Ueno', 'Published in 2020, this work explores themes of おたくの隣りはエルフですか？ 1.', 2020, NOW(), NOW()),
('おたくの隣りはエルフですか？３', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13184075-L.jpg', 'Meguru Ueno', '男子高生・犬童とお隣りさんの超世間知らずエルフ騎士・スルトとの異世界交流は、相変わらずハプニングばかり！ スルトの実家で婚約者を演じるハメになった犬童。豊満ドラゴンメイド・ファフニールに風呂場で迫られ、漢を見せる！（？） そんな犬童に、満天の星の下、ついにスルトがキスを‥‥！？ 凛々しいエルフ騎士に唇を狙われたり、えちえちに豹変した女生徒とバブみプレイしたり、異世界系ブレイブラブコメ、今日も爆裂さくれつ中！', 2020, NOW(), NOW()),
('Bibi Blocksberg', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/15113873-L.jpg', 'Olivia Vieweg', '###German-language description: Endlich Urlaub für Bibi und Miyu?! Wäre das nicht schön? Einfach mal die Füße baumeln lassen und die Sonne am Strand genießen! Wie praktisch, dass die diesjährige Klassenfahrt nach Okinawa geht, das Insel-Paradies im Süden Japans. Doch aus den Urlaubsträumen wird so schnell nichts – denn das Böse lauert auch hier hinter jeder Palme. Nur eine waschechte Junghexe und eine Geisterjägerin können die Reise retten! ---------- ###English-language description: When a new student from Japan shows up at Bibi Blocksberg’s school, she fits in immediately. But Bibi’s suspicious; she knows Miyu’s hiding something, and she’s determined to find out what! Bibi’s journey takes her all the way to Japan, and while learning about all the new rules and magic in this foreign land, she realizes that maybe she and Miyu can be friends after all!', 2022, NOW(), NOW()),
('Manga Reportage', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/11887652-L.jpg', 'Atsuhiko Nakamura', 'Tells the story of eight Japanese men, aged 30 to 50, who have never had sex. (Source: MyAnimeList)', 2016, NOW(), NOW()),
('おたくの隣りはエルフですか？ 2', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/14420661-L.jpg', 'Meguru Ueno', '異世界との交流が始まった日本。平凡な男子高生・犬童の日常は、隣りの部屋にエルフの姫騎士・スルトが引っ越して来てから崩壊した。 次々と襲いくる異世界美女＆美少女たち！　魔法少女にサキュバス管理人に女神まで、くんずほぐれつ絡まれまくりで、犬童の理性も操も大ピンチ！？', 2020, NOW(), NOW()),
('Black Clover T25', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/10504808-L.jpg', 'Yūki Tabata', 'Published in 2020, this work explores themes of Black Clover T25.', 2020, NOW(), NOW()),
('Black Clover T25', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/10504809-L.jpg', 'Yūki Tabata', 'Published in 2020, this work explores themes of Black Clover T25.', 2020, NOW(), NOW()),
('おたくの隣りはエルフですか？４', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13184076-L.jpg', 'Meguru Ueno', '臨海学校の肝試しで、クラス１の巨乳美少女・猪ノ瀬に告白される犬童。二人の距離は、心も体も縮まって‥‥！？ ほかにもヤンキー女神・エポナに気に入られたり、悪魔・メフィストフェレスに搾精をおねだりされたり、犬童に空前のモテ期到来！！！　エルフ騎士スルト、ヤキモチでやきもきですか！？', 2021, NOW(), NOW()),
('その着せ替え人形は恋をする 3', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/14425549-L.jpg', '福田 晋一', 'With their first cosplay event a success, Wakana and Marin are already thinking about their next big project! But complications arise when JuJu, one of Marin’s favorite cosplayers, comes calling…at Wakana’s house! There’s also the little matter of Marin’s newfound feelings for her partner in crime… When Wakana ends up at Marin’s place for an impromptu anime screening, it turns out the pair have the house to themselves! Will Marin be able to control her emotions, or will she let it all hang out?!', 2019, NOW(), NOW()),
('スーと鯛ちゃん2', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/15111203-L.jpg', 'こなみかなた [Konami Kanata]', '###German-language description Neue Katzenabenteuer von »Kleine Katze Chi«-Autorin Konami Kanata Sue ist schon eine etwas betagte Hauskatze, die bei ihren Besitzern ein rundum glückliches und friedliches Katzenleben führt – bis der aufgeweckte junge Kater Tai-chan einzieht. Der schwarze Wirbelwind fegt fröhlich und stürmisch durchs Haus und lässt Sue keine ruhige Minute mehr. Trotz des Altersunterschieds wird das ungleiche Katzenpaar schnell unzertrennlich. - Witziger Slice-of-Life-Manga über den chaotischen Alltag von zwei Katzen - Komplett in Farbe und westlicher Leserichtung – ideal für Manga-Einsteigerinnen - Die Serie gilt als noch nicht abgeschlossen - Ideal für alle ab 6 Jahren', 2020, NOW(), NOW()),
('異世界おじさん 1', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/14029028-L.jpg', 'Shindeiru Hotondo', '17年間の昏睡状態から目覚めたおじさんは、異世界からの帰還者だった……。甥っ子たかふみと共同生活を始めたおじさんが語る、新感覚異世界＆異文化コメディ！', 2018, NOW(), NOW()),
('その着せ替え人形は恋をする 4', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/12780417-L.jpg', 'Shinichi Fukuda', 'The cosplay team that started out with a bewildered Wakana and a passionate Marin has itself a new collaborator, the legendary JuJu! As the preparations for Marin and JuJu’s group cosplay steadily progress to completion, the team gears up for their photoshoot…but before that can get underway, Wakana must let the cat out of the bag about the big secret he’s been keeping from the girls: another cosplayer wants in on the action!', 2019, NOW(), NOW()),
('To LOVEる―とらぶる― 17', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13630609-L.jpg', 'Saki Hasemi', 'Published in 2010, this work explores themes of To LOVEる―とらぶる― 17.', 2010, NOW(), NOW()),
