('らんま⁠1/2 21‐22', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/15135362-L.jpg', '高橋留美子', 'Fathers know best, unless they''re Ranma''s. Genma promised Ranma''s mother that he would make sure the boy grew up manly - or else he would commit ritual seppuku! which makes for an awkward - and deadly - reunion, when Nodoka shows up and catches sight of her "son" in girls'' clothing. Plus more love is in the air with a new cheerleading suitor, Akane''s making fortune-telling mochi, more on Happosai''s affair with ladies'' undies, and an original story that inspired Ranma 1/2: deperately seeking shampoo!', 2015, NOW(), NOW()),
