('Robot vs Alien', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/10586802-L.jpg', 'Khairul Nizam Khairani', 'A living liquid metal was found inside a meteorite that fell to earth. A scientist escaped the metal and hid it in Zaqwan’s bag. Unexpectedly, it has symbiosis with Zaqwan allowing him to manipulate the metal into a weapon. The Malaysian Public Security Force (KAMAL) led by Captain Shamsir has hunted down Zaqwan for knowing the potential of the metal. At the same time, a mysterious robot appears who also hunts for Zaqwan to get the liquid metal. Can Zaqwan face an unexpected enemy to protect himself and his friends?', 2019, NOW(), NOW()),
