('If I understood you, would I have this look on my face?', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13178699-L.jpg', 'Alan Alda', 'The actor and founder of the Alan Alda Center for Communicating Science traces his personal quest to understand how to relate and communicate better, from practicing empathy and using improv games to storytelling and developing better intuitive skills.', 2017, NOW(), NOW()),
('Addictive disorders in medical populations', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/8613688-L.jpg', 'Norman S. Miller', 'This book has a much wider focus than traditional books written about drug and alcohol addictions. This unique book is written by medical specialists who diagnose, treat and research addictive disorders in their specialities. Thus, it meets the needs of the typical medical practitioner who wants to learn about and treat patients with addictive disorders in their practices. Because alcohol and drug problems are so prevalent and affect medical conditions profoundly, the medical specialist will improve their knowledge and skill to diagnose and treat addictive disorders in their specialties. Drug', 2010, NOW(), NOW()),
