('The Lincoln project', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/8844941-L.jpg', 'Dan Gutman', 'Four very different kids are picked by a mysterious billionaire to travel through time and photograph some of history''s most important events. This time, the four friends are headed to 1863 to catch Abraham Lincoln delivering his famous Gettysburg Address. They''ll have to work together to ask the right questions, meet the right people, and capture the right moment. And most important, not get caught!', 2016, NOW(), NOW()),
