('Eager 2 Cook : Healthy Recipes for Healthy Living', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13480640-L.jpg', 'E2M Chef Connect LLC', 'Published in 2022, this work explores themes of Eager 2 Cook : Healthy Recipes for Healthy Living.', 2022, NOW(), NOW()),
('If I Die Before I Wake', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/12604006-L.jpg', 'Eli Shaw', 'Published in 2019, this work explores themes of If I Die Before I Wake.', 2019, NOW(), NOW()),
