('Old Testament Readings & Devotionals', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/13643329-L.jpg', 'C. M. H. Koenig', 'Published in 2021, this work explores themes of Old Testament Readings & Devotionals.', 2021, NOW(), NOW()),
