('101 Rules Of Thumb For Low Energy Architecture', 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/7869394-L.jpg', 'Huw Heywood', 'This title sets out the essential elements of low energy architecture in a fresh, intuitive way. With reliable, simple rules that provide new ideas and refresh the designer''s palette, each page focuses on a single piece of advice along with an illustration. There are also plenty of tips and more detailed information for those who wish to dig deeper.', 2013, NOW(), NOW()),
